The paper discusses the challenges associated with connecting smart contracts with the outside world, which involves issues related to security, data consistency, and efficiency. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of cryptography (cs.CR), distributed computing (cs.DC), digital libraries (cs.DL), software engineering (cs.SE), or databases (cs.DB). The focus on data feeds and their integration with web services also supports these categories.
